#<P>Hotel reservations may be made by calling the Four Queens at 
#800-634-6045 and asking for the "ATLARGE 2020" rate.  The ATLARGE rate 
#is $22/$49 (weekday/weekend) and should be available between 8/3 and 8/8 
#(subject to change.) -->
	} else {
